snippet.title: Starshot : Space Circus Fever - early Game Trailer (1998) Nintendo 64/PC (Windows)
snippet.description:
Starshot : Space Circus early trailer
Developed by Infogrames UK
Published by Infogrames UK
(Ocean Software  Ltd was bought by Infogrames in 1996 and renamed Infogrames UK in 1998)
Year : 1998 (trailer), 1999 (game).
Systems : PC (Windows), Nintendo 64.

Titles : 
Space Circus (Working Title)
Starshot : Space Circus Fever (US)
Starshot: Panique Au Space Circus (FR)
Starshot: Panik im Space Circus (GER)
Starshot: Paniek in het Space Circus (Dutch)

Trailer  found on the 'Hexplore'  game disc (1998)
